{
  "stem": "521.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you educated?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in the school in Hungary, each and every religion was supposed to be taught in the school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Jews were having the rabbi, or a good substitute for a rabbi, who was teaching in school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a rabbi of our city teaching me when I was 17 and 18, the last two years of the high school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's a sad story about this rabbi, who was a very talented man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He has written about four or five books on religious affairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in 1944, he had a chance to escape from deportation because there were Jewish organizations, a Zionist organization, who helped certain people who were either Zionist or committed or talented people, they thought are worth saving.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, I'm not going to leave my flock in trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If they are going to be deported, I'm going to be deported.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Soon after, when they have arrived-- when he has arrived to Auschwitz, he got into a kind of a unit where they were putting the dead persons' clothing in order-- like the shoes are in one part, the clothing into [INAUDIBLE], children's were in the other [INAUDIBLE]-- children and old people were gassed immediately.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day, he has found his 12-years-old son's shoe, and this broke him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I am not-- I'm not surprised.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then he perished pretty soon after.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Danish Freedman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think Danish in English is Daniel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Freedman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was well respected, even though he was only in his 40s at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think he was-- well, he was the rabbi when I was [? bar mitzvahed ?] at-- in '35, and-- 1935.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was conducting himself very respectably.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
